{"tid":2405811,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［年經］對住窮撚講「恭喜發財」係咩居心","createTime":"2021-02-12T16:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T02:37:46.000Z","uid":142824,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4b2c13cb7a564220dfc0d368012d1136c4607983","tid":2405811,"uid":142824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T16:19:29.000Z","msg":"拜年就緊係上啲三五九識七、成年都無關心過嘅公公婆婆姨媽姑姐屋企坐下，睇下佢有冇武肺啊使唔使扔入老人院俾啲心理變態嘅職員玩下咁。<br />\n<br />\n一見到面，唔使講啦一定要射啲恭賀說話出黎俾大家劣下鳩咁啦。身體健康呢啲行野唔講，青春常駐擺明係玩野嘅大家心知肚明，但係我到而家都唔明，點解要對住個住爛溶溶公屋嘅親戚講「恭喜發財」？<br />\n<br />\n恭喜，係代表你有個樣野，先會比人恭喜。例如你買GME高位放期權，咁連登社工咪會同你講「恭喜發財」囉。你sp有咗，咁我咪同你講「恭喜你有身紀」囉。<br />\n<br />\n但係住得公屋/負資產私樓又無幾個錢（唔包公屋富戶/28歲以下公屋單人住戶），講你食餅其實係喜頓雜餅（仲要唔係星級裝），恭喜發財其實係串鳩佢&mdash;&mdash;你啊，發咗財都係咁樣咋。<br />\n<br />\n有啲人會話，一句恭祝說話啫，禮儀黎嘅啫，都係祈求對方可以發大財。如果照呢個邏輯，麻煩你同啲結婚十年，終於響35歲之前有咗BB，然後五秒之後難產嘅高齡產婦面前講，「喂～恭喜你有身紀啊^_^」，跟手再同佢解釋話「其實呢都係恭賀說話啫，希望你未來會有BB啫哈哈。」睇下佢老公打唔打撚死你？<br />\n<br />\n所以如果你仲有憐憫之心，新年唔好再咁黑心，同窮撚講「恭喜發財」。"},{"pid":"084b2bd3016e552025b522af7c1e4bce196355e3","tid":2405811,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T16:21:23.000Z","msg":"其實應該講祝你「不撈而獲」"},{"pid":"d4c471ffa891b309382d8e40d93b444e3b08e45f","tid":2405811,"uid":329977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T16:21:54.000Z","msg":"同我諗法一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺唔覺得「恭喜發財」呢句野有缺陷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2404856\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2404856</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1d5e61fa5b3ec260329081f212a98dd7ebf6413d","tid":2405811,"uid":142824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T16:22:01.000Z","msg":"BTW 我GME 中位放咗期權，賺咗五年人工，麻煩大家對細佬講「恭喜發財」ok？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 恭喜發財<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />恭喜發財"},{"pid":"1b9f2c81405d81e10d9f5bb167a07378fb0eaf4c","tid":2405811,"uid":299433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T16:33:01.000Z","msg":"恭喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35413e9747ab0d762f9f23f5b997935e826d4667","tid":2405811,"uid":140495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T02:21:08.000Z","msg":"樓主仲寫唔寫文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8c4df04d1b90a26f18110a62db7f4288d750f8","tid":2405811,"uid":67329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T02:22:39.000Z","msg":"恭喜發財係一種祝福<br />\n<br />\n當然 對窮撚黎講同佢講一個錢字<br />\n都當你攻擊緊"},{"pid":"642d9e43ebf80b8296276bfa4a95cf22ab33365b","tid":2405811,"uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T02:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VzyaCho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVzyaCho.jpg&h=b998f1c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c5f4f29bced7cd4489ac20d4287bf8146cab46a","tid":2405811,"uid":362504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T02:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e0ef83d39376f05ad0e67c1f9c3cc4069d8263","tid":2405811,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T02:37:46.000Z","msg":"有趣<br />\n人哋無睇死你，係你限制你自己嘅。"}]}